Invocation Name: faith baptist church
des: Listen to live services from Faith Baptist Church in Ft. Pierce, FL. Service times: Sundays 10:00 am, 11:00 am, 12:45 pm and Wednesdays at 7:00 pm. Hear soothing music outside of service times. You can pause and play by saying "Alexa, pause" and "Alexa, resume." Just say "Alexa, stop" when you're done for the day.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
